            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Perpetuae <expan><abbr>me</abbr><ex>moriae</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>securit</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Tib</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> Euphras IIIIIIvir <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustalis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>negotiat</abbr><ex>or</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>artis purpurariae qui vixit <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> LXXVI Seniliae Lasciva<lb break="no" n="5"/>e coniugi et Claudis Fortunensi <lb n="6"/>et Epigono <supplied reason="lost">et</supplied> Apro filiis vivos vivis <lb n="7"/>fecit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nur handschriftlich überliefert. (B): ILS; CIL 03, 05824: Z. 1: [d. m. et] perpetuae securit. Tib. Cl. Euph[r]a[tes] IIIIIIvir Aug., nego[t.]; Z. 4: Clau[d.]. ILS: Zeilenfälle nicht angegeben.</p>
            </div>
